These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
City: boston, prague, hannover, colone
Movie-Genre: action, superhero, sports, family
1. Movie-Genre:family is on the left of City:hannover##1
2. City:boston is on the left of Movie-Genre:superhero##1
3. City:colone is in an odd position##4
4. Movie-Genre:sports is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:family##3
5. City:boston is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| City   | boston | prague | colone | hannover |
| Movie-Genre        | action | superhero   | family | sports    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
Flower: balloon-flower, azalea, rose, iris
Sport: swimming, soccer, skiing, sailing
1. Flower:azalea is on the left of Flower:iris##1
2. Sport:swimming is on the left of Sport:skiing##1
3. Sport:skiing is in an odd position##4
4. Sport:swimming == Flower:balloon-flower##1
5. Sport:soccer is on the right of Sport:skiing##1
6. Sport:swimming == Flower:balloon-flower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Flower   | rose | balloon-flower  | azalea  | iris |
| Sport   | sailing    | swimming | skiing | soccer    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
Sport: cricket, weightlifting, water-polo, climbing
Game: bridge, snooker, poker, go
1. Sport:climbing is on the left or right of Game:go##3
2. Sport:water-polo is in an even position##4
3. Game:go is on the left or right of Sport:weightlifting##3
4. Game:go is on the right of Game:poker##1
5. Game:bridge is in an odd position##4
6. Sport:weightlifting is on the right of Sport:water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Sport          | climbing | water-polo | weightlifting    | cricket      |
| Game   | poker        | go     | bridge | snooker |

