2. Nationality:brazilian is on the left of Nationality:italian##1
3. Cigar:cain is on the left of Cigar:bolivar##1
4. Nationality:nigerian == Cigar:bongani##1
5. Cigar:cain is on the left or right of Nationality:italian##3
6. Nationality:indian is on the right of Nationality:italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| Cigar   | bongani | cain | bolivar | tiparillo    |
| Nationality     | nigerian | brazilian  | italian     | indian |

