2. Nationality:nigerian is on the right of Movie-Genre:satire##1
3. Nationality:american is between Nationality:nigerian and Movie-Genre:disaster##2
4. Movie-Genre:satire is in an odd position##4
5. Nationality:american is on the left or right of Nationality:nigerian##3
6. Movie-Genre:superhero is on the left or right of Nationality:polish##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre      | superhero       | disaster   | satire | documentary |
| Nationality   | french | polish | american        | nigerian    |

