4. House:victorian is on the left of House:craftsman##1
5. House:craftsman is on the right of Music-Genre:country##1
6. House:victorian is in an even position##4
7. House:art-deco == Music-Genre:metal##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
