.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
Movie-Genre: animation, disaster, sports, drama
Sport: volleyball, tennis, handball, rugby
1. Movie-Genre:disaster is in an even position##4
2. Movie-Genre:disaster is on the left or right of Sport:volleyball##3
3. Sport:tennis is between Movie-Genre:animation and Sport:volleyball##2
4. Movie-Genre:disaster is on the far left or far right##3
5. Sport:handball is on the right of Movie-Genre:drama##1
6. Sport:handball is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Movie-Genre         | animation | sports   | drama | disaster |
| Sport   | rugby          | tennis | volleyball         | handball  |

 